<comment><![CDATA[An attribute  to specify what is the specialised lending type of an exposure.

According to CRR3 art 147 (8): Those exposures shall be assigned to the exposure class referred to in paragraph 2, point (c)(ii), and shall be categorised as follows: “project finance” (PF), “object finance” (OF), “commodity finance” (CF) and “income-producing real estate” (IPRE).’]]></comment>
